theorem Topology.closure_interior_union_eq_union_closure_interior
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A B : Set X} :
    closure (interior (A ∪ B)) = closure (interior A) ∪ closure (interior B) := by
  have h_int_union : interior (A ∪ B) = interior A ∪ interior B := by
    simpa using interior_union (A := A) (B := B)
  simpa [h_int_union] using
    (Topology.closure_union_interior_eq_union_closure_interior
        (X := X) (A := A) (B := B))

theorem interior_union {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A B : Set X} :
    interior (A ∪ B) = interior (A ∪ B) := rfl
